profileResult.name: Entity proxies
profileResult.description: The technology under test is able to store stubs for entities to use on relationships when the full entity is not available.

requirementResults.name: Store entity proxies
requirementResults.description: The technology under test supports the storage of metadata instances that are proxies for instances from other repositories in the cohort.

requirementResults.name: Retrieve entity proxies
requirementResults.description: The technology under test supports the command to retrieve a proxy instance of a metadata instance.

requirementResults.name: Entity proxy locking
requirementResults.description: The technology under test ensures metadata instances that are proxies for instances from other repositories can not be updated.

requirementResults.name: Retrieve entity proxies
requirementResults.description: The technology under test ensures that proxy instances are removed from its repository with integrity when the master copy is deleted.
